text:
Aerial footage has shown people sunbathing in London parks, ignoring social distancing advice amid the #coronavirus outbreak. 

The health secretary has warned outdoor exercise could be banned if people continue to flout the lockdown rules. 

More  👉 https://t.co/gMkhrHG7IT https://t.co/D9wQ6ZKLDK
